== Overview ==
The Photonic SV adds an extra layer to the shields depth making it more resistant to hits. It also comes with a rather attractive stand to sit it on.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Photonic SV Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
